&lt;p&gt;Have you got what it takes to be a discharge practitioner and be involved in a safe and quality discharge planning?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Can you take the pressure of discharging patients in a timely and smooth manner?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an individual who are flexible, multi-tasking, passionate, and has very good communication skills that can make a positive difference to the discharge experience of our patients?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If so, then we are waiting for you to join us in Hardy ward Team at Northwick Park Hospital as our Discharge Practitioner?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Working 37.5 hours per week over 5 days, you will hold your own caseload of patients and be able to expand your knowledge of complex discharge issues, whilst contributing positively to the standard of discharge planning in the Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameJincy Mary JoseJob titleElderly care Nurse PractitionerEmail addressjincyjose@nhs.netTelephone number02088695070&lt;/p&gt;
